'''Peers''' was a [[Captain/Legends|captain]] in the [[Corellian Defense Force/Legends|Corellian Defense Force]], often abbreviated to the CDF. In [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]], the CDF received reports about dangerous animals from [[Circus Horrificus/Legends|Circus Horrificus]] roaming the [[Corellia/Legends|Corellian]] landscape. As tracking and removing these creatures could have turned into a time-consuming endeavor, Peers used public mission terminals to hire a civilian hunter to track down and kill the beasts.<ref name="SWG:CHLaM">{{SWGcite|exp=AED|type=terminal||Circus Horrificus Left a Mess}} on Corellia</ref>

